":"英国英格兰可瓦爾","Cornwall, England":"英国可瓦爾","Devon, England":"英国戴文","lifeSummary":"当Joan Trelawny于1427年出生在英国英格兰可瓦爾时，她的父亲Sir John Trelawny MP30岁，母亲Lady Joanna Helligan32岁。她于1432年与Baron Thomas Upton of Treloish在英国可瓦爾厄普頓结婚。他们至少是4个儿子和1个女儿的父母。她去世于1464年在英国英格兰享年37岁。"},"hr":{"1427–1464":"1427.–1464.","1423–1460":"1423–1460","1406–1470":"1406–1470","1432–1489":"1432.–1489","1435–1491":"1435.–1491","1457–1503":"1457.–1503","–1517":"–1517","1397–1467":"1397–1467","1395–1473":"1395–1473","1473":"1473","1395":"1395","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1491":"1491","1415":"1415.","1503":"1503","1435":"1435.","1457":"1457.","1467":"1467","1489":"1489","1423":"1423","1432":"1432.","1464":"1464.","1397":"1397","1517":"1517","1406":"1406","1427":"1427.","Buckerell, Devon, England":"Buckerell, Devon, England","Upton, Cornwall, England":"Upton, Cornwall, England","England":"Engleska, United Kingdom","Tournay, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, Engleska, United Kingdom","Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"cs":{"1427–1464":"1427–1464","1423–1460":"1423–1460","1406–1470":"1406–1470","1432–1489":"1432–1489","1435–1491":"1435–1491","1457–1503":"1457–1503","–1517":"–1517","1397–1467":"1397–1467","1395–1473":"1395–1473","1473":"1473","1395":"1395","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1491":"1491","1415":"1415","1503":"1503","1435":"1435","1457":"1457","1467":"1467","1489":"1489","1423":"1423","1432":"1432","1464":"1464","1397":"1397","1517":"1517","1406":"1406","1427":"1427","Buckerell, Devon, England":"Buckerell, Devon, Anglie","Upton, Cornwall, England":"Upton, Cornwall, Anglie","England":"Anglie, United Kingdom","Tournay, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, Anglie, United Kingdom","Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, Anglie","Devon, England":"Devon, Anglie"},"da":{"1427–1464":"1427–1464","1423–1460":"1423–1460","1406–1470":"1406–1470","1432–1489":"1432–1489","1435–1491":"1435–1491","1457–1503":"1457–1503","–1517":"–1517","1397–1467":"1397–1467","1395–1473":"1395–1473","1473":"1473","1